compiler directives
declare global variables
function prototypes
main function
	declare local variables
  	configure IO Ports
  	Configure crossbar
 	initialize timer
 	begin infinite while loop
 		Calibrate accelrometer
 		if pound key has been pressed
 			read keypad values and update gains
 		average gx = stores average value of accel in x
 		average in new value for x
 		average gy = stores average value of accel in x
 		average in new value for y
 		display new values to the lcd

 		convert accelerometer in x to rough angular movements
 		use Porportional control to turn accordingly

 		if accelerometer in y is roughly constant to measured value of gravity
 			stop drive motors
 		else run full power
 	end infinite while loop